title: Learning English more than 100 book collection
description:
More than 100 books for those who want to learn English Language (a lot of International books and also a lot of books for Russian learners)

This package includes many famous bestsellers like In Use series, NewHeadway, Thomson, Quirk and many many more. And it also has audios, videos, CD's.

This one will be useful for beginners, students, teachers (for everyone)

List (just some of them for example because i can't make large descriptions on TPB):

SpeakOut - Longman (2012 1st ED)(6 levels from Starter to Advanced)
OUTCOMES - Heinle (2011 1st ED)(5 levels from Elementary to Advanced)
New Headway - Oxford (~2009 all 1st ED books and some 3d and 4th)(6 levels from Beginner to Advanced)
Quirk A comprehensive grammar of the English language 1985
English Grammar in Use (Essential) (3rd Ed) (2007) + CD
English Grammar in Use (Essential) Supplementary Exercises (second edition)
Murphy R. English Grammar in Use. 2012 4-ed. + CD
English Grammar In Use (Intermediate) Supplementary Exercises (3rd Ed) (2004)
Hewings Martin. Advanced Grammar In Use With Answers. 3rd edition - 2013 + CD
A. J. Thomson A Practical English Grammar 4th ED
A. J. Thomson A Practical English Grammar Exercises 2 books
